					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player has the last Netherstone, triggering a dialog with the Emperor to point them towards the Netherbrain. Main pieces of info he communicates here:\r\n\r\n- The player has met the requirements needed to enter end game\r\n- This trip is one-way\r\n- Frame the upcoming confrontation with the Netherbrain in Morphic Pool \r\n- Where to find the boat"
